from INR. This species was previously recorded from 
<collectingRegion country="Argentina" name="Corrientes" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">Corrientes Province</collectingRegion>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Keffer, S. L." box="[293,450,614,640]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" pagination="117 - 215" refId="ref51319" refString="Keffer, S. L. (1997) Systematics of the New World waterscorpion genus Curicta Stal (Heteroptera: Nepidae). Journal of the New York Entomological Society, 104 (3 - 4), 117 - 215. [1996]" type="journal article" year="1997">Keffer (1997)</bibRefCitation>
